<li>Though we can't celebrate with you physically, our hearts are with you. Happy Birthday.</li>
<li>Happy birthday, [Name]. We think of you and your wonderful life every day.</li>
<li>Today, we raise a glass to your wonderful life and memory. Happy birthday.</li>
<li>You live on in our hearts and memories. Happy birthday, dearest [Name].</li>
